{"tid":844274,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"香港將會有廉航直飛印度新德里","createTime":"2018-10-01T17:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T08:59:39.000Z","uid":48958,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fd93f963bfd66e751f50472552290618f740e98a","tid":844274,"uid":48958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T17:34:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://flyday.hk/61217/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fflyday.hk%2F61217%2F&d=dAXwXkv%2Fm4ok0mA0guYe6QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=291edc69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://flyday.hk/61217/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ab953d998f9e69c6bbb44ce40497ac6be6d5cc","tid":844274,"uid":213441,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T17:39:55.000Z","msg":"飛去俾咖哩佬強姦？"},{"pid":"c2ed0ca85ce7ba735ed02473d885ff69c8a239de","tid":844274,"uid":48958,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T17:40:28.000Z","msg":"Sorry應該貼埋內容出嚟<br />\n<br />\n印度呢個千年古國，充滿著各種稀奇古怪嘅事物同埋文化，想去探索嘅話機會嚟喇！印度香料航空新設咗香港直航新德里航線，11月至19年3月出發，直航來回新德里$1,870 (連稅$2,225)咋！直航印度嘅機票一向好貴，呢個價錢比其他對手平左一半有多！票價仲已包咗20公斤行李！即刻tag多幾個朋友一齊買飛去喇！<br />\n<br />\n去程：SG32 07:40-10:50<br />\n回程：SG31 22:45-06:40<br />\n<br />\n出發日期：11月22日至19年3月31日<br />\n訂飛日期：即日起<br />\n停留期限：無限制<br />\n<br />\n訂飛網址：<a href=\"http://www.spicejet.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.spicejet.com&d=dAXwXkv%2Fm4ok0mA0guYe6QHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=de894750\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.spicejet.com</a>"},{"pid":"ed94f99f250464ca46a4709d02e2a358006134cd","tid":844274,"uid":186152,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T18:17:29.000Z","msg":"比狗搭"},{"pid":"87ae13620fe8c778927d37d3c921a2234f3064c0","tid":844274,"uid":42636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T18:19:48.000Z","msg":"想比印度人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb858b2ad764ee164bff0bcfbc9aa61d0f39897a","tid":844274,"uid":80110,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T18:24:00.000Z","msg":"用737飛咁撚遠 仲要飛咖哩國 你坐撚埋我嗰分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cafeabd42546ec31e63e5fc8230091fe15a1a40e","tid":844274,"uid":80110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T18:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用737飛咁撚遠 仲要飛咖哩國 你坐撚埋我嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"99c0b121d00cdd47509e4b9443cd4468eeb95e7f","tid":844274,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T18:25:59.000Z","msg":"如果三年後重有，可一戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848ed735112a7d99b8a6c086905dcee31ed4f899","tid":844274,"uid":62023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T18:26:12.000Z","msg":"去印度？ 咪搞啦"},{"pid":"388d29ef3ad1e9c63ce74d63d382e5173acb565e","tid":844274,"uid":86585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T18:51:43.000Z","msg":"正 可以瘋狂比印度咖喱味圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24361aea56b7231330fa1dcda57d45aa672d8abe","tid":844274,"uid":48958,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cafeabd42546ec31e63e5fc8230091fe15a1a40e","tid":844274,"uid":80110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T18:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用737飛咁撚遠 仲要飛咖哩國 你坐撚埋我嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:40:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/150702/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/150702/page/1</a><br />\n飛機在飛行的途中，若遇上一些突發事故，例如機械故障、氣候不佳等，基於飛安的考量通常會選擇迫降在鄰近的機場。而印度廉航班機卻因為廁所發出惡臭因此迫降。<br />\n<br />\n根據《鏡報》報導，印度廉價航空公司香料航空編號SG192的客機，當時機上載著184名旅客，原定由印度的邦加羅爾（Bangalore）飛往德里（Delhi），途中卻因為機上廁所散發出極度惡臭，蔓延至機艙，使機上乘客難耐，因此中途迫降於海德拉巴（Hyderabad）機場。<br />\n<br />\n飛機降落後，經過了約莫三個小時的清潔，才又再度啟程飛往目的地德里。<br />\n<br />\n飛香港會唔會都...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bc4480c366dc8b2483042ffab3b4c3e75ed12a","tid":844274,"uid":78873,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:47:16.000Z","msg":"想屌印度妹好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b8936b22002fd4597d85f9d5d6aadee94bbcbf","tid":844274,"uid":165598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T07:48:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"75e9b31c065ebaae508626c712dc54cfdce08d82","tid":844274,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T05:44:16.000Z","msg":"印度佬飛過嚟酷刑聲請，每月袋幾千fat fat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n張超雄又贏🤙"},{"pid":"1a45013766a865a41e9f49989f47daa17ad0d77f","tid":844274,"uid":47470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T08:59:39.000Z","msg":"其實幾吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 2000幾直航，仲要去新德里唔係孟買<br />\n但呢個唔係一次promotion咋咩"}]}